            <title><![CDATA[No Man's Sky gets space wreck salvaging and expanded ship building as its busy year continues]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/no-mans-sky-gets-space-wreck-salvaging-and-expanded-ship-building-as-its-busy-year-continues</link>
